Vorteile/Features

* distributed (offline, mistakes, -- commit rights (RST), submit
  changes as email) - efficient storage with full history
* instant (easy) branching and merging
* speed
* flexible (sub commands)
* optimized: large file sets, complex changes, trial branches, being very fast
  (Randal's talk), being robust

